      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPLASH OF PAYNT (3) ran second last start at this track over 1780m, beaten 3.5 metres. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Stepping up a level this time but he is good enough to take this out. SWEET AGENDA (10) has been a bit hot and cold and that continued last start when she finished third, beaten 11 metres, in a nice return to form here over 2040m. Draws out a little on the second line and may need luck at some point but her recent form is good enough to win a race of this calibre. BORELLA NZ (2) disappointed last time when eighth over 1780m at this circuit. Can bounce back from the low draw. TIGER SHIRL NZ (1) must be respected after scoring last start by 2.25 metres at Marburg over 1850m. Can go back-to-back from the pegs.",
